values (
  $cfseed$crossfit-rules-and-standards-advisor$cfseed$,
  $cfseed$CrossFit Rules and Standards Advisor$cfseed$,
  $cfseed$Use when the user asks what a CrossFit competition rule, movement standard, scoring method, or penalty means for a specific competition and season, interpreting USER-SUPPLIED or authorized current rule text. Expects the event, season, division, and the rule text or a citation. It uses only a matching season, cites the source, separates official rule from interpretation, and never fabricates standards. Excludes workout strategy, owned by crossfit-competition-workout-strategist, and design, owned by crossfit-workout-designer.$cfseed$,
  $cfseed$personal$cfseed$,
  $cfseed$competition$cfseed$,
